{"tid":396440,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"［慎入］屋企個櫃發霉點算好？","createTime":"2017-09-11T16:00:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-13T11:04:42.000Z","uid":83739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f726de85d4b29fcf4a6e6e6bff89ae9e6e1daaad","tid":396440,"uid":83739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T16:00:30.000Z","msg":"自從夏天來臨，樓下個冷氣機成日搞到屋企周地水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 為免床底堆衫發霉，買左好多吸濕器<br />\n<br />\n最近發現床下底裝衫個櫃角落頭，好似發霉...於是心血來潮將所有衫搬出來，反轉個櫃......<br />\n原來櫃底發曬霉，好Q核突<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n以下係個櫃的圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/11/235844_64e50819d0e24a602dcfe8f56507e373.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F11%2F235844_64e50819d0e24a602dcfe8f56507e373.jpg&h=8c0798f2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/11/235844_eb2fc2bf6f9690b4390f7c91b6c518cb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F11%2F235844_eb2fc2bf6f9690b4390f7c91b6c518cb.jpg&h=260878d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n聽講要曬太陽...有冇巴打絲打知道要曬幾耐同埋點斷尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2655ec9199ccb71cd580fdd00a31167e38c1494b","tid":396440,"uid":130673,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T16:04:03.000Z","msg":"俾返個櫃人啦"},{"pid":"257009cabd337add1b9d6ff0dbe6b1c8d6265448","tid":396440,"uid":26506,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T16:12:29.000Z","msg":"Kill it with fire"},{"pid":"a55f69ac7620bb4b0845a57ea3ccc79b67e6f20c","tid":396440,"uid":99989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite