":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T04:48:54.000Z","msg":"唔知板心有冇霉定係表面霉。 表面就清理左佢， 入面都霉埋就有可能將來生蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4452ad34d9d7675e1e113b1bf000230677e70093","tid":396440,"uid":83739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T03:45:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔知板心有冇霉定係表面霉。 表面就清理左佢， 入面都霉埋就有可能將來生蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 生蟲！<br />\n櫃入面角落頭有霉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 是咪已經玩完"},{"pid":"f2f09b1c007273408388f59e82dccb1366235b96","tid":396440,"uid":83739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T03:48:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>換啦 <br />\n新櫃放吸濕</blockquote><br />\n張床新買一年都唔夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最衰夏天樓下開冷氣開到我屋企成灘水搞到霉左下面三個拉櫃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c48af4339f38036711a4c22f29b0764e3346897","tid":396440,"uid":83739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T03:52:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>講還講<br />\n我屌你老母你放乜撚野圖？</blockquote><br />\n對唔住大佬！<br />\n但我講左慎入架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n大撚哂 貼link啦</blockquote><br />\nOn9仔 貼乜撚野link 我鐘意就咁睇喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁撚核突都鐘意睇 c hing 睇黎平時睇唔少奇特野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實有得較所有圖都唔好自動顯示<br />\n你手動㩒先會load圖"},{"pid":"80c927f6763bbf0a6118c5597b20d084328c5381","tid":396440,"uid":83739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T03:53:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Kill it with fire</blockquote><br />\n真心覺得呢個最work<br />\n但好驚燒鬼左間屋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\